reviews.review_text:
SMOKAH great, nice upbeat version of franklins
but start to finish a solid show, sound quality
is great, great crowd
The Good Ole' Spectrum I remember this night. It was great! I was in section Z in the Spectrum hanging-out when Tennessee Jed came blaring thru. I was really happy. I miss shows.
